            <div class="item active">
                <table style=" width:80%" ; align="center">
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <img src="~/images/humain.png" alt="human" style="height:500px ;position:center;margin:auto;">
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            <h3 style="color:black">Human</h3>
                            Human are the most common species in Sierra. They are well fitted in any position and no real stereotype follow them.
                            In Sierra during the Undead Emperor's reign , the other race considered Humans racist but in fact most of those who left the empire integrated in other societes just fine. Human usually live until 80 years and for the most lucky 120.
