                    </tr>
                </table>
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h3 style="color:black"></h3>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
                <table style=" width:80% ;" align="center">
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <img src="~/images/bebokkan.png" alt="Bebokkan" style="height:500px;margin:auto;">
                        </td>
                        <td>

                            <h3 style="color:black">Bebokkan</h3>
                            Bebokkans are a Clerian race , it mean they are half human, half beast; Bebokkans look like lizards, snakes, crocodiles , or other reptiles.
                            In Sierra they are mostly found in Ondelbel, living of hunting and training .
                            In Hera they can be found everywere but most of them are in the south were the temperature are hotter.
                            They live as long as a Human


